title: Prem Ratan Dhan Payo
casts: Salman Khan, Sonam Kapoor, Anupam Kher, Neil Nitin Mukesh, Sanjay Mishra, Swara Bhaskar, Deepak Dobriyal, Arman Kohli, Manoj Joshi, Samaira Rao, Karuna Pandey, Sucheta Khanna
description: While recovering from an assassination attempt four days prior to his coronation, a stern prince is replaced by a joyful and generous doppelgänger.

title: Paharganj
casts: Lorena Franco, Bijesh Jayarajan, Neet Chowdhary, Rajeev Gaursingh, Karran Jeet, Rajesh Sharma, Gautam Kurup, Poonam Mathur, Salman Khan, Manish Devkush
description: In the underbelly of a Delhi neighborhood, a woman’s search for her missing lover collides with drugs, death and a coach grappling with his demons.
